 of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/83338/', '', 'Desipramine', 'Amoxapine, Viloxazine', 1767369485);
