ether they are receiving an acetylcholinesterase inhibitor.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/83391/', '', 'Aducanumab', 'Desvenlafaxine, Isocarboxazid, Oxitriptan, Tryptophan, Vortioxetine, Milnacipran, Levomilnacipran, Vilazodone, Esketamine', 1767369485);
